In side this folder there is the landb gem file.

To install it:

	a) Copy the file localy to puppet master.
	b) sudo gem install ./landb...(gem path)
	c) enjoy :)
	
There are some other things that must pre exist:

	a) sudo yum install ruby-devel
	b) sudo yum install rubygems
	c) sudo gem install rake
	d) sudo gem install savon 